.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
Never point a Samba server at itself for password serving\&. This will cause a loop and could lock up your Samba server!
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
